{
  "stem": "18654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they came into the village singing these songs and he went out and probably told them to get off in no uncertain terms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the next day he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he came back after some time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can't remember the length of time, that I remember I was the first one to see him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I screamed, papa is here papa is here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother couldn't believe it and she came running out of the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were then left alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I think it became too difficult to live there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think the end of it, '38, we moved to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm told, bearing in mind I was very young, and I was-- I'm told that there were about six Jewish families, and all called Lowenthal, which was my mother's maiden name.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't really tell you much about them, except we used to have a good community relationship with each other, especially on the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would visit each other's homes and suchlike.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember one little Jewish girl called Steffi, but I really remember very little about the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't even remember school days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although I have some pictures of my early school days, I don't remember anything about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was Pesach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember when Pesach was over, the matzahs that remained we used to make into parcels, and we used to take to our non-Jewish friends, who used to seem to like having matzahs for some unknown reason.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember Hanukkah, that was very important, because the table was laden with presents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was rather, I suppose, spoiled in that respect because my sister wasn't interested in toys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I used to have all hers as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What other festivals can I remember?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
